# postcss-tag-to-id
> root tags to id

## Install

```bash
npm install --save postcss-tag-to-id
```

## Usage
__`source.html`__
```html
  <about>
    <h1 id="homepage">About</h1>
  </about>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    vnjs.on('load',()=>{})
  </script>
  <game-over>
    <h1 class='game-over'>Game Over</h1>
  </game-over>
  <style type="text/css">
    .game-over{}
    #homepage{}
    about{
      color: cyan;
    }
    
    game-over{
      padding: 15px;
    }
  </style>
```

__`gulpfile.js`__
```javascript
const
  gulp                        = require('gulp'),
  postcss                     = require('gulp-postcss'),
  concat                      = require('gulp-concat');


gulp.task('css', function () {
   let plugins = [
        require('postcss-tag-to-id')({prefix: "#vnjson__"})
       
    ];
    gulp.src(['./src/screens/**/*.css'])
      .pipe(postcss(plugins))
      .pipe(concat('style.css'))
      .pipe(gulp.dest('./dest'))

});
```

__`output.css`__
```css
.game-over{}
#homepage{}
#vnjson__about{
  color: cyan;
}
    
#vnjson__game-over{
  padding: 15px;
}

```
## Options
```js
{
  prefix: 'string'
}

```

